    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3190840/extras/5b4bc4ce088cfe7a516f51a7b2c19b8e.avif?t=1748273294\" width=608 height=248 /></span>Most people know nothing about this exciting world that exists all around us, in every pond, stream, ocean, and even the smallest puddles! Guided by Aggi from 'Aggi and the Mystic Boots', customize your own cell and take them on a journey of survival through vibrant environments.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3190840/extras/fdfdd1b795d3e000a4f7a0c6748a9b5b.poster.avif?t=1748273294\" width=608 height=400 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3190840/extras/fdfdd1b795d3e000a4f7a0c6748a9b5b.webm?t=1748273294\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3190840/extras/fdfdd1b795d3e000a4f7a0c6748a9b5b.mp4?t=1748273294\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Customize Your Cell</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Choose its shape and pattern.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Select how it feeds.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Attach a flagella or two.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Or choose from a selection of real world examples.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >When you're happy with your cell send it out into the world and see it survive alongside a multitide of other organisms.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3190840/extras/fca743611ab7bb79607738edd4e734d8.poster.avif?t=1748273294\" width=608 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3190840/extras/fca743611ab7bb79607738edd4e734d8.webm?t=1748273294\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3190840/extras/fca743611ab7bb79607738edd4e734d8.mp4?t=1748273294\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Learn Real Science</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Find all the different organisms in the environment to unlock journal pages and read about the wonderful world of microbiology. You can also earn stars for surviving and discovering a wide variety of cells in each habitat.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3190840/extras/1ec6f317c235d34fb49159709bf061dd.poster.avif?t=1748273294\" width=608 height=400 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3190840/extras/1ec6f317c235d34fb49159709bf061dd.webm?t=1748273294\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3190840/extras/1ec6f317c235d34fb49159709bf061dd.mp4?t=1748273294\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >A Game For All Ages</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >With minimalist gameplay akin to looking down a microscope and with no content locked behind a skill wall, Aggi's Tiny Friends can be enjoyed by all budding scientists!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
